en_US: Please enter the last 5 digits of the transfer hash.
zh_TW: 請輸入轉帳哈希值末 5 碼
zn_CN: 请输入转帐哈希值末 5 码

en_US: There are no available payment channels, please try again later or contact customer service.
zh_TW: 當前無可用支付渠道，請稍候再試或聯繫客服。
zn_CN: 当前无可用支付渠道，请稍候再试或联系客服。

en_US: Failed to get the link to recharge \n Please change the recharge channel or contact customer service.
zh_TW: 充值連結取得失敗\n請更換充值渠道或聯繫客服
zn_CN: 充值连结取得失败\n请更换充值渠道或联系客服

en_US: If the order is correct, please enter the above verification code.
zh_TW: 如訂單無誤，請輸入以上驗證碼
zn_CN: 如订单无误，请输入以上验证码

en_US: You have been logged out, please log in again
zh_TW: 你已被登出，請重新登入
zn_CN: 你已被登出，请重新登入

en_US: 1. Please be sure to provide true information to facilitate the verification of the transfer data.
zh_TW: 1. 請務必提供真實資訊，以利核對轉帳資料。
zn_CN: 1. 请务必提供真实资讯，以利核对转帐资料。

en_US: 2. Please write the required information in the Remittance Remarks to speed up the recharge process.
zh_TW: 2. 請在匯款備註寫入要求資訊，加速充值流程。
zn_CN: 2. 请在汇款备注写入要求资讯，加速充值流程。

en_US: There are many people paying at the moment, please try again later!
zh_TW: 當前支付人數眾多，請稍後再試！
zn_CN: 当前支付人数众多，请稍后再试！

en_US: Order creation failed, please contact our customer service.
zh_TW: 訂單建立失敗，請聯繫客服
zn_CN: 订单建立失败，请联系客服

en_US: 1：Payment was not successful, please try to pay several times.
zh_TW: 1：支付不成功，請多次嘗試支付。
zn_CN: 1：支付不成功，请多次尝试支付。

en_US: 2：Can not pull up the payment order, is due to pull up the order more people, please try to pull up the payment several times.
zh_TW: 2：無法拉起支付訂單，是由於拉起訂單人數較多，請多次嘗試拉起支付。
zn_CN: 2：无法拉起支付订单，是由于拉起订单人数较多，请多次尝试拉起支付。

en_US: 3：Please contact our online customer service if the recharge is successful but not arrived.
zh_TW: 3：充值成功未到賬，請聯繫在線客服。
zn_CN: 3：充值成功未到账，请联系在线客服。

en_US: We are trying to get the recharge URL, please wait...
zh_TW: 正在努力取得充值網址，請稍候...
zn_CN: 正在努力取得充值网址，请稍候...

en_US: Please click to open the recharge page.
zh_TW: 已取得充值網址，點擊開啟充值頁
zn_CN: 已取得充值网址，点击开启充值页

en_US: Failed to get the website address \n please choose a new channel or contact customer service
zh_TW: 取得網址失敗\n請重新選擇渠道或聯繫客服
zn_CN: 取得网址失败\n请重新选择渠道或联系客服

en_US: Please make sure you fill in the correct information to avoid affecting the payment.
zh_TW: 綁定後不可更改，請確認資料填寫正確，避免影響到帳。
zn_CN: 绑定后不可更改，请确认资料填写正确，避免影响到帐。

en_US: Please enter the name of the branch (optional)
Please enter your bank card number
Please enter your bank card number
The password should be the same for the second time
zh_TW: 二次驗證密碼輸入應相同
zn_CN: 二次验证密码输入应相同

en_US: Do you really want to quit the game?
Please complete the card binding before withdrawing money.
zh_TW: 請完成銀行卡綁定，方可進行提款
zn_CN: 请完成银行卡绑定，方可进行提款

en_US: Insufficient liquidity, please continue to play
If you have not reached the limit \n need to pay the withdrawal fee of {fee} (estimated)\n Click to confirm to send out the withdrawal order.
zh_TW: 未達成流水限額\n需自行負擔提現手續費 {fee} 元(預估)\n點擊確認送出提現訂單
zn_CN: 未达成流水限额\n需自行负担提现手续费 {fee} 元(预估)\n点击确认送出提现订单

en_US: Input amount must not be less than {amount}.
Input amount must not be greater than the remaining balance
zh_TW: 輸入金額不得大於餘額
zn_CN: 输入金额不得大于余额

en_US: Input amount is in wrong format
Withdrawal application has been completed, you can check the current application status in the withdrawal log.
zh_TW: 提款申請已完成，可於提款紀錄查詢目前申請進度。
zn_CN: 提款申请已完成，可于提款纪录查询目前申请进度。

en_US: Withdrawal fee {fee} % will be charged for withdrawal before reaching the limit.
zh_TW: 未達流水限額提現需支付提現手續費 {fee} %
zn_CN: 未达流水限额提现需支付提现手续费 {fee} %

zh_TW: 密碼為 8-20 位字母及數字
zn_CN: 密码为 8-20 位字母及数字

en_US: Account is 6~12 digits alphabetic and numeric
zh_TW: 帳號為 6~12 位字母及數字
zn_CN: 帐号为 6~12 位字母及数字

en_US: Greetings to our valued users \n Global Gaming invites you to download the APP to enhance your gaming experience.
zh_TW: 尊貴的用戶您好\n環球遊戲邀請您下載APP，提升遊戲體驗。
zn_CN: 尊贵的用户您好\n环球游戏邀请您下载APP，提升游戏体验。

en_US: This password is only for the first time you log in to the APP \nPlease be sure to change your password after logging in.
zh_TW: 此組帳密僅提供首次登入APP使用\n請務必在登入後，更換帳號密碼。
zn_CN: 此组帐密仅提供首次登入APP使用\n请务必在登入后，更换帐号密码。

en_US: You have been logged out, please log in again
zh_TW: 你已被登出，請重新登入
zn_CN: 你已被登出，请重新登入

en_US: Please try again later, sorry for the inconvenience.
zh_TW: 請稍後再試，造成不便請見諒
zn_CN: 请稍后再试，造成不便请见谅
